org.bukkit.attribute

インタフェース Attributable

  • 既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    Ageable, Ambient, Animals, ArmorStand, Bat, Blaze, CaveSpider, Chicken, ComplexLivingEntity, Cow, Creature, Creeper, EnderDragon, Enderman, Endermite, Flying, Ghast, Giant, Golem, Guardian, Horse, HumanEntity, IronGolem, LivingEntity, MagmaCube, Monster, MushroomCow, NPC, Ocelot, Pig, PigZombie, Player, Rabbit, Sheep, Shulker, Silverfish, Skeleton, Slime, Snowman, Spider, Squid, Villager, WaterMob, Witch, Wither, Wolf, Zombie

    public interface Attributable
    Represents an object which may contain attributes.

    • メソッドのサマリー

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      AttributeInstance getAttribute(Attribute attribute)
      Gets the specified attribute instance from the object.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • getAttribute

        AttributeInstance getAttribute(Attribute attribute)
        Gets the specified attribute instance from the object. This instance will be backed directly to the object and any changes will be visible at once.
        パラメータ:
        attribute - the attribute to get
        戻り値:
        the attribute instance or null if not applicable to this object
